Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.48,Main Title 1,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Second Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.48,Main Title 2,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 11
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:05.35,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,How are the two omelette wraps?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:07.44,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,This one's with chili sauce,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:08.73,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and this one's with basil sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.66,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,I can make it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:12.36,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:14.61,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys ever stop eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:16.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So, Shiomi-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:19.07,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,About this... Stagiaire thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.07,0:00:19.91,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What is that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:24.54,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,"Stagiaire" is a French word \Nmeaning "resident."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:26.68,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It's a program to send
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.68,0:00:30.17,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,high school first-years to various \Nbusinesses in the food industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:34.57,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,They can be high-end restaurants, food\Nmanufacturers, or even public organizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:37.13,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,They cover a wide range.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:40.43,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It's a formal curriculum intended to \Ngive students practical experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.93,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:47.02,Main Dialogue,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt even professionals \Nwould be better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.86,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something to take lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:51.02,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,All the Stagiaire partners
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:54.42,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,have all agreed to take on students \Nbecause they trust the academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.74,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,If you cause any problems that would \Nnegatively impact Totsuki's reputation,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:00.70,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,you might even get expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:02.56,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:04.46,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is the kind of school I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.34,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So I can go out to work \Nin a different kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:10.17,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Out into the world\N outside of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:14.63,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,So you pass if you do your job \Nwithout causing problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:16.60,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,The criterion for passing it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:20.64,Main Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,is to make a "visible mark" \Nduring your time in residency.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:23.79,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,A visible... mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:27.08,Days Later Sign,Sign 0126,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}A Few Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:32.90,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, so the first training site\N is tackled in pairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:34.65,sign_2228_35_Training_Program,Sign 0134,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Training Program Guide \N {\fs18}Yukihira Soma-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:41.58,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira... Soma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:14.86,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's give it our best, Miss Secretary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.92,Episode Title,Sign 0314,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}The Stagiaire
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.38,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:19.04,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:22.82,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get through the Stagiaire \Nthrough my efforts alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:23.76,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:27.69,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I wonder what kind of \Nrestaurant we'll be sent to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:28.85,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.30,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Since the almighty Totsuki Academy \Nis telling us to go there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.38,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's some ritzy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:35.31,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.40,sign_5163_49_Western_Restaura,Sign 0338,0000,0000,0000,,Western Restaurant\N Mitamura
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:36.40,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:39.08,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what I thought it'd look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.49,Main Dialogue,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna make us wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.48,Main Dialogue,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,I can't finish eating in five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:44.17,Main Dialogue,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,Cancel my order!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:44.83,Main Dialogue,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:45.47,Main Dialogue,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:45.91,Main Dialogue,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:48.51,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, sorry, so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:53.14,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two Totsuki students,\N by any chance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:04:01.05,sign_5626_61_Western_Restaura,Sign 0358,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Western Restaurant Mitamura \N Third Chef Owner \N {\fs22}Mitamura Mamoru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:58.40,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wish you hadn't seen that \Nembarrassing scene just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:01.05,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mitamura, \Nthe third owner of this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.83,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:07.79,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I am Arato Hisako. I will be here \Nfor a week for the Stagiaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.14,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure I have much to learn,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.27,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,so I appreciate your having me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.05,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yukihira Soma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.02,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:16.77,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:19.98,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Arato-san and Yukihira-kun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.73,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sorry to cut to the point, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.27,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,...can I have your autographs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:25.95,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:29.34,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're students of {\i1}the{\i0}\N Totsuki Academy, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:33.65,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,You might become world-renowned \Nall-star chefs in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.33,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,He reminds me of someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.71,Main Dialogue,Tomita,0000,0000,0000,,Soma-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:42.64,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not any chef to be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.97,sign_6791_79_Arato_Hisako___L,Sign 0444,0000,0000,0000,,Arato Hisako \N {\fs28}Loyalty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.97,sign_6791_80_Yukihira_Soma__D,Sign 0444,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira Soma \N{\fs20}Diner Yukihira's on Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.56,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Arato, how much longer are you gonna take?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:48.65,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me when I'm \Nstill changing clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.03,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your manners?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:55.64,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it feels new to stand in the kitchen \Nwithout wearing my Yukihira T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:04:59.94,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:02.90,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You look pretty good in an apron, Arato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:03.65,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:07.79,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Nit's my first time talking to you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:10.16,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You were always with Nakiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.04,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.54,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The next time you see Nakiri—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:14.53,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.11,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot go back to Erina-sama anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:22.66,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I have no right, after being \Ndefeated in the Autumn Elections.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:24.71,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:26.48,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You lost to Hayama, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:26.94,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:27.51,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:31.51,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama is invincible and undefeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:34.48,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,If a loser like me stays at her side,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.48,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll demean her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:39.94,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.15,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.36,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there was \Na commotion here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.58,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.34,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it all we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.14,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so first off, Arato, you can—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:54.84,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:55.83,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.21,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get on a high horse just because \Nyou have practical experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:02.14,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I've taken classes where \NI had to cook in teams, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:05.17,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I had no problems during camp \Nfinishing tasks that required speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:08.16,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to have \Nany problems in the Stagiaire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.93,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,But what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.08,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,They were all situations that didn't involve
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.93,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,dealing with an endless stream \Nof orders, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:15.15,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:20.40,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,H...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:21.02,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,H...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.65,Main Dialogue,Staffs,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:23.36,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.57,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.53,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Completely full in the blink of an eye?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.36,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:27.90,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.28,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,A barrage of orders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.24,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,One Omelette A Set and another D Set.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.65,Main Dialogue Top,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Three Special Lunch Sets, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:33.26,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea it'd be this bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:37.00,Flashback Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Before, most of our customers \Nused to be locals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:41.17,Flashback Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Then our nearby train station \Nbecame a bullet train stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.74,Flashback Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,All the people taking the \Nbullet train now rush here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:47.01,Flashback Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,place their orders, and ask \Nto settle the check at once, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.76,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why they can't handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.39,Main Dialogue,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's my order?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:53.01,Main Dialogue,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,I need it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.26,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the A and D Sets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:57.18,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on. It'll be five more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.92,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,We need to wash dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:00.31,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.68,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough clean dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:04.11,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:06.80,Main Dialogue,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.43,Main Dialogue,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to run to catch my train!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:09.86,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Please come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:16.74,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:18.45,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.21,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,The next wave, right as I thought \Nwe finally had things handled!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.21,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,This is like a battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.92,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a moment's rest \Nbetween each wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:30.55,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Here are some orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.48,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Table 1 wants a special sandwich,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:33.32,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,two French toasts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.05,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and three coffees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.44,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The coffee should be after their meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:36.87,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Table 3 wants two beef stews,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:37.59,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,two Napolitans,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.11,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,one coffee, two iced coffees,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:39.94,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and one melon soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:41.76,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Napolitans should have no green peppers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.70,Main Dialogue,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,The food's kind of slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:45.31,Main Dialogue,Customers,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to make the train at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.11,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Arato, can you handle the customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:47.77,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.20,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Table 4's order is up,\Nincluding the Napolitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:54.28,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:55.87,Main Dialogue,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.97,Main Dialogue,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,I ordered a cheeseburger with cheddar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.21,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:00.03,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make the right o—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:00.45,Main Dialogue,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:01.69,Main Dialogue,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:01.69,Main Dialogue Top,S,0000,0000,0000,,Arato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:04.04,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,There's bad communication between \Nthe kitchen and the servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.19,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Can you go check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:09.68,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Giving me orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.39,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Who does he think he is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.64,Flashback Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Everything about you... is too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.10,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,But what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:21.14,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,They were all situations that didn't involve
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.98,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,dealing with an endless stream \Nof orders, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:27.48,Flashback Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't show my face to Erina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.70,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.78,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:40.60,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:41.91,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,We made it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:43.44,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,That was wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.54,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, we wouldn't have made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.25,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.07,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki's students sure are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:54.72,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He has practical experience, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.24,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,What? We're talking about you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:01.30,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,By dinnertime, you were all up to speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.18,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,You're a quick learner, and flexible, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.09,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,You were a huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:08.98,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:12.16,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?! How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.46,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:16.32,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up the good work tomorrow, too, Arato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.70,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.74,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.42,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.67,sign_13587_204_French_Restauran,Sign 0928,0000,0000,0000,,French Restaurant Excellent \N {\fs28}Head Chef Kasayama
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.67,Main Dialogue Top,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.77,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I am saying that I won't wash dishes \Nor anything of that sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.97,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I believe delegating trivial tasks to me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:38.47,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,is nothing other than \Na foolish error in judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:42.97,Main Dialogue,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a student. Get over yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:47.60,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Soma-kun! Things are \Nlooking rocky on my end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.36,sign_14108_212_Third_Day_of_Tra,Sign 09350,0000,0000,0000,,Third Day of Training
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.36,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you were a huge help today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:54.34,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,It was a great idea to accept residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:09:59.76,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a photo of this restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:00.86,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.20,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,It's from back when \Nmy dad used to be the chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:07.83,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,I still remember how he was worshiped \Nby all the local regulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:12.20,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Your restaurant does have a wide selection,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.61,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,and you season your dishes very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.50,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.34,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,That's about the only thing I'm proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:19.90,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try my best to work toward \Nthat ideal restaurant from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.86,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,What're you slacking for, Yukihira Soma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.31,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,We're not done cleaning yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:33.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is this good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.28,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving a visible mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:39.49,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.26,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.63,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,The program's going quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:46.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:49.66,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I wonder \Nhow the others are doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:51.53,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of restaurants\N they ended up in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.75,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Erina-sama is doing well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:58.03,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,even without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.25,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful, Chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.80,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The dishes have been refined \Nabove and beyond what they used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:07.03,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The redesigned course menu \Nis novel and bold, too! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.53,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you'll get a Michelin star \Nnext year for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:12.10,Main Dialogue,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you, it's an honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:17.00,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama, please check the taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.86,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama, sorry to keep \Nyou waiting on the prep work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.45,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Saucier, you are 50 seconds behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.12,Main Dialogue,Sau,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:24.58,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.23,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Please serve it to the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:26.79,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:30.58,Italics Dialogue,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,My castle... was taken over... \Nby that little bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:33.61,Italics Dialogue,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,before I even knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:36.02,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Chef Kasayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.63,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,About the main dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:41.25,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I believe the texture can be improved
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.59,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,if it is poached at a \Nslightly lower temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:46.85,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,There are about twelve other issues \NI'd like to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:49.81,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Would that be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.81,Main Dialogue,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.69,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Then first, regarding the hors d'oeuvre...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:02.71,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be something I can do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:07.16,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this just isn't cutting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:09.84,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.54,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,What do you find lacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:12.92,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,They make solid food,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:15.96,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,their staff are all nice,\N and they care about their restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:19.71,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help them as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:21.09,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:22.80,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is this good enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:23.55,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:26.74,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That restaurant isn't where \Nyou really want to be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.14,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I do think that the restaurant has to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.73,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.61,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.56,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.74,sign_18229_272_Fourth_Day_of_Tr,Sign 1241,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Fourth Day of Training
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.74,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Arato-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.26,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of the delivery slips today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:47.32,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. I'm already on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.90,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:54.00,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,This restaurant has to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.25,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, Yukihira Soma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:13:00.71,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That restaurant isn't where \Nyou really want to be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:03.13,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:04.97,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Remember who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.30,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:09.43,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we came, sales have gone up, \Nand complaints have gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:14.20,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,If... we leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:14.98,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.19,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,They'll revert back to their old ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.34,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, adding more bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:24.97,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,during crunch time will \Nhelp keep the restaurant running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.16,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not really solving the root problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.66,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we should let \Nthings stay the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:33.83,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,We're holding an emergency meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.71,sign_19546_292_Emergency_Staff_,Sign 1336,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency Staff Meeting \N Discussion: Future Direction for\N Western Restaurant Mitamura
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:39.77,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:42.12,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,the Stagiaire will end with \Nmy only having done trivial tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:45.72,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything amazing like Nakiri-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.80,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,but I have to be more useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.20,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the next batch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:51.26,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:14:00.27,sign_20080_299_Fill_This_In,,0000,0000,0000,,In Preparations
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.27,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Let's advertise a part-time job right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.88,sign_20147_300_Emergency_Staff_,Sign 1401,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency Staff Meeting \N Discussion: Future Direction for\N Western Restaurant Mitamura
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:04.55,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find new help before \Nthe Totsuki students leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:09.16,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,But do you think we can easily \Nfind people who can fill their shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:12.70,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Should we cut down the menu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:17.49,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,The large menu has become a liability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:19.92,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,If you print a new menu, \Nkeeping only the customers' favorites—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.24,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:23.75,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,There are recipes in there that \Nare from my grandfather's day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:26.24,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep on the way you have, \Nthis restaurant will eventually go under—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:30.45,Main Dialogue,Staffs,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're grateful for your help and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:33.16,Main Dialogue,Staffs,0000,0000,0000,,But making such a huge change...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:36.53,Main Dialogue,Staffs,0000,0000,0000,,We've been working here \Nsince the previous owner's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:39.62,Main Dialogue,Staffs,0000,0000,0000,,If we change the menu, \Nit wouldn't be Mitamura anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:43.93,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you feel sorry for the customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:46.23,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they chose \Nthis place to come into,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:49.29,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,they can't get the food they ordered. \NIt's not even about the taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.39,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.30,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Mitamura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.24,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of restaurant \Ndo you want this place to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.50,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:00.71,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want you to consider...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.21,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.26,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:04.88,Main Dialogue,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:09.34,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,About the second course, the fish salad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.09,Main Dialogue,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,What, you too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:12.91,Main Dialogue,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to washing dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.31,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.43,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:17.43,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:19.94,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:25.35,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be nice if customers could \Nchoose how much sauce they want to pour on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:29.95,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,The dishes that come in either\Ntend to have a lot of leftover sauce,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.93,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,or a lot of leftover vegetables
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.20,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,if customers used bread to soak up the sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:39.91,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,She found something to improve, \Njust from washing dishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.31,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,But it might be difficult to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:45.36,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,It'll mean more work \Nfor the hall and kitchen staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:46.04,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:49.74,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Serving the sauce in a saucière has been
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:52.68,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,a widespread practice\Nin France for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:56.55,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Reverting to such a tradition \Nmay actually be quite novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.52,Main Dialogue,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:01.23,Main Dialogue,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,The customers are coming here to eat {\i1}my{\i0} food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.86,Main Dialogue,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about the amount of sauce—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:03.85,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.60,Main Dialogue,Kasa,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.90,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,A customer's requesting more sauce...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.82,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Please come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:23.46,sign_23460_349_Thank_You_for_Yo,Sign 1621,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Thank You for Your Business. Due to Circumstances, \NWe Are Changing to Reservations Only. \N Western Restaurant Mitamura
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.46,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Going to reservations only?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:27.09,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Mitamura's food is good. \NThere's no questioning that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:31.38,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your careful work and the \Nlarge menu, customers are always satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:35.20,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,But these virtues have become faded
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.39,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,because of the changes in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:40.27,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So I think this is a possible \Noption for you to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.98,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad for customers \Ntrying to drop in, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:45.34,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Reservations only, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:49.44,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to say, but will it actually work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:52.95,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,It's a huge risk to turn away customers \Nwho find their way to our door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:57.47,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we suddenly have to change \Nhow we've been doing things now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.08,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,If the circumstances have changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.54,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,and you don't also change, \Nyou won't be able to move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.84,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,If there is something \Nyou really want to pursue,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:09.57,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,you should cling to it without \Nworrying about appearances!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:12.36,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I believe this restaurant has great potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:15.05,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.89,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not us who'll be \Nmaking that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:23.98,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's the man at the top, right? Mitamura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:28.31,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What is it you want to pursue as the chef?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:30.77,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.80,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Shimizu-san, thank you for the reservation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.28,Main Dialogue,Shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, sorry for not coming by for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.16,Main Dialogue,Shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed really busy recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:41.44,Main Dialogue,Shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,so I found it hard to drop in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:43.27,Main Dialogue,Shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you're only allowing reservations,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.12,Main Dialogue,Shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,I came rushing back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.78,Main Dialogue,Shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,I want the usual Napolitan, \Nand two side dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:48.89,Main Dialogue,Shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.74,Main Dialogue,Mita,0000,0000,0000,,Cut back a bit on the salt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:53.77,Main Dialogue,Shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,You know me, third-generation chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.59,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.98,Main Dialogue,Shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.73,Main Dialogue,Shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,The food here tastes \Njust as good as I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.44,Main Dialogue,Shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,May I have coffee afterward, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.25,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:18.53,Italics Dialogue,Nishino,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It seems they've overcome one of the \Ncriteria for passing the Stagiaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:18.53,sign_26246_386_Totsuki_Academy_,Sign 1815,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Totsuki Academy \NAcademic Affairs Division \N {\fs24}Nishizono Kazue
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:22.40,Italics Dialogue,Nishino,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just enough to handle \Nthe job you were given.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:25.91,Italics Dialogue,Nishino,0000,0000,0000,,You have to figure out what you can do \Nto improve the restaurant and take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.87,Italics Dialogue,Nishino,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first step in the Stagiaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.62,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking pretty blue \Non the first day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:33.09,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but you look like you're \Nfeeling a bit better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.24,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.49,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to waste in idle talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.68,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,you can work harder, Yukihira Soma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.17,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you enjoyed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:45.56,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,It's, "Thank you! Please come again!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.14,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start using your own catchphrase!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.73,Main Dialogue,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,You've passed the first Stagiaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:53.73,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.92,Main Dialogue,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Your work was faultless, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.48,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.59,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Where were they watching us from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.11,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki sure is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:04.87,Main Dialogue,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Information about the next training location \Nshould be delivered by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.85,Main Dialogue,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.71,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Arato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.71,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to go back to \NNakiri's place soon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:16.89,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:17.79,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:20.38,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up. I can hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:27.85,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.89,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Why's this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.50,Flashback Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have a lot of luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.06,Flashback Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.94,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why someone with your talent \Nhas been unknown for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.41,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What? This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:47.84,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,What was the score on your \Nhigh school division entrance exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:50.81,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it was really low!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:53.04,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell her I got the worst grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:59.03,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't manage to make \Nmy way back from that on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:03.27,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to survive camp \Nand enter the Autumn Elections
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:06.76,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,all thanks to everyone \Nat the dorm and Soma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:09.33,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,When I first saw Soma-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:12.73,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I made up my mind to stay \Nas far away as I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:14.60,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,but we somehow became friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.29,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't talk any more about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.28,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.98,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I said something \Nthat got on her nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:25.78,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Nakiri-san, \Nyou're always with Arato-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:27.70,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.23,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is something wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.47,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hisako...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:32.96,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,See, Hisako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:35.96,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,The cherry blossoms are so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.75,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,You should come over here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:42.35,Flashback Dialogue,GirlH,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that would be improper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.13,Flashback Dialogue,GirlH,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay behind you, Erina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:47.01,Flashback Dialogue,GirlH,0000,0000,0000,,I am your aide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:50.92,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hisako...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:55.03,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,What I wanted back then was for you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.82,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.59,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I still lack confidence somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:03.40,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've been too complacent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:07.02,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I was fine as long as I could \Nwalk behind Erina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:09.91,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:13.20,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So, why are you stressing out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:14.41,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Did you even hear what I said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:16.29,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The answer's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:20.05,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, try to become someone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:24.01,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,who can walk beside her \Ninstead of behind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:27.71,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to Hayama, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:30.34,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So let's beat him someday, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:35.48,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,But... I lost. I don't have the right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:38.52,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something \Nyou really want to pursue,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:40.67,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,you cling to it without \Nworrying about appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:42.09,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:46.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and these belong \Nto one of my dorm mates,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:49.14,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but she said she could spare them for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:54.50,sign_31411_460_With_Heart,Sign 2151,0000,0000,0000,,With Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.57,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Nakiri she could read them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:54.51,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but it's hard to find time \Nto drop them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.57,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a great opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.96,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Take them to Nakiri, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:00.77,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Arato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:02.77,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drop them on the way, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:07.93,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira Soma...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:11.47,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.27,0:22:14.27,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:31.12,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same way, Arato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:38.43,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, my cooking may have just\N been me chasing after my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:41.90,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take my time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:44.50,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,checking out the cooking world outside \Nof Yukihira, with wide-open eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:48.97,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm gonna shine a new light \Non my own cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.61,0:22:50.57,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:52.59,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the next Stagiaire?!
